//object Literal
for checking property by using ? mark. It will check the command and after it run the code.
 for delete an variables in object use keyword "delete"
 example:let alien={
    name:'arun',
    brand:'js',
    laptop:{
        ram:4,
        cpu:7,
    }
}
delete alien.laptop
console.log(alien.laptop?.ram)

